    dc:description "Figure 16. Legs of Araneus spp. male holotypes, prolateral view A-D A. wanghuai sp. nov. E-H A. yangchuandongi sp. nov. I-L A. yuboi sp. nov. A, E, I legs I B, F, J legs II C, G, K legs III D, H, L legs IV. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
